Package: invasimap
Title: invasimap: A Novel Framework to visualise trait dispersion and assess species invasiveness or site invasibility
Version: 0.0.9
Authors@R: 
    person("First", "Last", , "first.last@example.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Provides a trait-based, site-specific workflow to quantify
    invasion fitness by combining predicted abundances, trait-based
    competition, and environmental matching. Includes tools to simulate
    invaders, compute interaction kernels, assemble impact tensors, and
    visualise trait dispersion.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
URL: https://github.com/macSands/invasimap,
    https://macsands.github.io/invasimap/
BugReports: https://github.com/macSands/invasimap/issues
